(piano music)

00:09.861 --> 00:12.989
(woman): ♪♪ Loneliness
comes to call ♪

00:13.030 --> 00:16.367
♪ As sometimes the sun ♪

00:16.408 --> 00:20.621
- ♪ Doesn't shine for us all ♪
- Christina?

00:20.663 --> 00:24.917
