Christina, it's Dr. Godfrey.

00:30.954 --> 00:33.207
- Can you hear me?
- ♪ Love needs a place ♪

00:33.248 --> 00:35.751
♪ To start ♪

00:35.793 --> 00:38.963
♪ And who knows who may hold ♪

00:39.005 --> 00:42.424
♪ The key to your heart ♪

00:42.466 --> 00:44.386
♪ Don't be afraid ♪

00:44.426 --> 00:48.557
♪ Of what all that extends ♪

00:48.597 --> 00:52.601
♪ Loneliness ends with love ♪

00:52.643 --> 00:56.189
♪ The greatest need ♪

00:56.231 --> 00:58.191
♪ Inside you ♪

00:58.232 --> 01:03.112
♪ Is the need to be understood ♪
